dct_title_s: Karta poleznyh iskopaemyh : kavkazskago kpaya = Mineral resources map, Caucasian edge
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by shading.; Shows locations of mines for antimony, bismuth, nickle, cobalt, quicksilver, manganese, iron, arsenic, pyrites and sulphur; also shows locations of prospect mines and smelters.; Kavkazskago Gornago Upravlen?ya = Caucasian Mountain Management Edition.
